import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import { Form, Col, Row } from 'react-bootstrap'

function ClientForm() {

    return(
        <Form>
<Form.Group>
  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      First Name
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Last Name
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Cell Phone
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Home Phone
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Email
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="email" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Address Line 1
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Address Line 2
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      City, State, Zip
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="City" />
    </Col>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="State" />
    </Col>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Zip" />
    </Col>

  </Form.Row>


  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Large Text
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Large Text
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>

  <Form.Row>
    <Form.Label column="lg" lg={2}>
      Large Text
    </Form.Label>
    <Col>
      <Form.Control size="lg" type="text" placeholder="Large text" />
    </Col>
  </Form.Row>
</Form.Group>

<Form.Check 
    type="switch"
    id="custom-switch"
    label="Confirmed Booking"
  />

</Form>

    )
}

export default ClientForm;
